Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,side. Yeah, it does. It has a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of, all that adrenaline,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all that excitement, all the
