Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,various things. Move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough fear for now. I'm scared
