Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,does. Anger, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,specializes in righteous anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,especially righteous anger.
