Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,important. No, it's not more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,important. It's just swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And pride. This is pride we were
