Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you feel superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a superior
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,elitism, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Politically elite, politically elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to be superior and it's fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get to be right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get to be better than other people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get to be special. You get to be noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you get to be mentioned on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you think it gives you status, at least
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the small, and makes you very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the payoff
