Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult to get
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,off it because you would have to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the narcissistic ego
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,would rather die than be humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather die than be humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather die than say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. And of course
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we know that spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is really based on humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because so much of spiritual
