Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,revelation. It's not the acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of new information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But putting that information to work
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you step back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you're walking along not thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,anything, it spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,comes to you.
