Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it spontaneously comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a break. That wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,logical. It's not something you read in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you have become. A certain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,caringness about life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one. After pride
