Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,pride
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip it because I can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't read it it can't be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, these
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,are confirmation of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The confirmation of spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've tested with kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you will get these answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God, divinity, Allah, by whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,name, the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all characteristics of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now here's where it makes a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,difference. You see, at 855,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to move
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to allness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The omnipotence, omnipresence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,omniscience, these
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,are all confirmable. You see that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness is 850. That's where
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I started. 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothingness. Nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great place, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,other than allness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This side of allness, nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody to be concerned about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. It's infinitely
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,marvelous. That's the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, seeing into one's self-nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is around
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,800 here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reality of witness-observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, is a good
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,place that anybody can start. Anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,can, by a little contemplation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and observation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,get to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that witnessing and observing is not
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,something that there's a personal you doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The personal you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity. We confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all these names
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and ways of holding divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Allah, Shiva, Krishna,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brahma, Vishnu, Durga,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Asvara, Rama,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,God of Moses and Abraham.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Christ, Christ Consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Purusha,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the Self with a capital S, the Atman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we calibrate and confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of these things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The angels and the archangels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said the archangel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,once an archangel thought of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,once an archangel had a passing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,notice. It was like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,being hit by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say, here's this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,archangel cruising by and he hears this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,prayer. I was in the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The very pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The pits of hell are worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Than I've ever read, described.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, Dante comes close to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This prayer arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the response was from an energy field of 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The vibration is still going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so it goes on from there on up to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think that this universe is an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity, the universe is expanding
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,New universes are being created at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With no limitation, with no end beyond time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just, your mind can't even stretch it, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Universes beyond these universes every second are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,stretching on into infinity forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A little silly to defy God, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, John the Baptist, this just confirms the spiritual realities and St. Paul, Tarsus, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The fall of Muhammad, of course, is what the world is experiencing the consequence of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:15:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years after he dictated the Quran, his consciousness suddenly dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's characteristic of many advanced spiritual teachers, pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But they get knocked off one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see a teacher calibrates at 580, 590, and then suddenly they're 160 and you read about them on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's a vulnerability, I think, that the forces which are not happy with truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the world being dominated by truth and integrity, look for some chink in the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for some chink in the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what I try to teach is the chinks that they, that are looked for at the various levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think students...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what happened to these teachers is their teacher did not forewarn them about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what the weaknesses are at the various level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I try to tell people, when you get into the 500s, when you get into the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you think you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the intellectual pride and the spiritual ego really starts to kick in in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 500s, you become very...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of love is attractive to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the pitfall there is seduction, seduction, and maybe half a dozen world-famous avatars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and teachers and they fell right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual, you know, sexual seduction of devotees, etc., exploitation of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the power to exploit, the exploitive teacher who starts to control people's personal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,lives, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, each level then has its own downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the list of living as well as dead spiritual teachers who were in a great place and crashed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is really disconcerting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't like to put it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing I knew it was on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't put it up for the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it up for students in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, the safety that we have in the world today is that we can calibrate the level
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of teachers, and therefore, I think that's very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't study a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who they are, unless I calibrated them to begin with, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to put your hands, your life, and your spirit, and your soul in the hands
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of somebody who you don't even know who they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're famous and they've got a million followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know spiritual teachers with millions of followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they're the walking reincarnation of Christ and they calibrate 195, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People give up everything and follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have, at last, a way to keep that from happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got just a few more for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is our thing working?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we already did this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We did this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we did the Gospels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, the current Gnostic thing is the Gospel of Judas, which was rejected
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time it was written as being heretical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the Gnostics were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gnostics themselves were heretical and somewhat aberrant in their teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice many things are extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think these are wonderful things to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the previous list, we had the Integrist teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Integrist writings, writings, the Rig Veda, the Rubbiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all things that we can easily put our hands on and they're accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So a spiritual student today has many advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got verification of teachers and verification of scriptures and writings, which the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,has never had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has never had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, when we say the chances of becoming enlightened in today's world, I'll reconfirm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,this again for the audience, is over a thousand times what it was in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The chances of people in this audience becoming enlightened are over a thousand times what
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it was even one generation ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank the Zohar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank the Yoga Sutras of Padañjala.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank all these people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank all these people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So very interesting, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go on one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we said Wang Po's teachings, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got one more slide to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the verses of the Old Testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to calibrate a scripture, because they are very variable, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Scriptures are written over hundreds of years, many generations, many contributors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What ended up in the Bible, you know, was by vote, and then the scribes, even as they're
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,writing it down, put in their own interpretations, changed the word here and there, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't really do the whole thing at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a composite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's many books.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you can do is calibrate the percentage they calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Old Testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only 10 verses that calibrate exactly to 1,000, 0.2% calibrate over 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that an interesting study you can go through and see what percentage of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, here we do the same thing with the Koran, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people say, well, that's in the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in the Koran?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything in the Koran...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be from the lowest to the highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about Surah 9-5, that's the sword verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you meet the infidel, cut his head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a religion of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to tell me it's a religion of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Read verse 30, Surah 34.4 in the Koran, and tell me if it's a religion of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill every infidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you glorify God is by killing every infidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut his head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't say slowly in the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a new addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Invented creative addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we have a whole different way now of understanding religion, what to put
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,our faith in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it's in the Koran or in the Bible doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Places of spiritual interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that is in truth versus falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that's a very interesting list.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was a fun list to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All the famous places around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these I've been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be able to calibrate a cathedral, calibrate Stonehenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stonehenge is at $5.99.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a bunch of stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunch of big rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it get to be $5.99?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we break for lunch now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She says we break for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we resume at what time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resume at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're breaking for lunch and we're resuming at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you for your attentiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this afternoon, this afternoon we'll do the new slides that we did, a run through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:22:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This afternoon we'll do the new slides, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception versus essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoiled rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoiled rotten with a group like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody probably knows where we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Janice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventy-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventy-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to get to the new slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritual experiences, oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we calibrate them, Der Gapuja Festival, is it 480?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Passover?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,485?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian Communion?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I knew that years ago when they blessed the host.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.70,0:24:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.01,0:24:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.01,0:24:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is really 600 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.07,0:24:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Satchitananda, that's 600 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.45,0:24:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's not many people around because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.93,0:24:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.93,0:24:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are always asking me, how many people are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.93,0:24:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.38,0:24:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.38,0:24:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.38,0:24:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.38,0:24:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.38,0:24:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.38,0:24:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.41,0:24:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.41,0:24:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.41,0:24:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.41,0:24:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are always asking me, how many people are on the planet, you know, 600 and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.41,0:24:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.41,0:24:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've counted them over and over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.84,0:25:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because at this level, about 50% of the people leave, and it's hard to explain why,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.34,0:25:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have permission to leave, and it's really sort of an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.83,0:25:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.83,0:25:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So enlightenment is really the levels from 600 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori, very often in meditations, around 585.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The near-death experience, 520, and, of course, the ultimate states are 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.36,0:25:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the Amazing Grace hymn, you should, at 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.70,0:25:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas itself is at 675.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let those who wish to demolish Christmas beware.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.00,0:25:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They will arouse my ire and my wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Prince of Peace, I'm going to blow them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Smudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.57,0:26:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Smudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.05,0:26:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Smudging.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.05,0:26:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.08,0:26:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Smudging is at 520.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.29,0:26:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's more than just a sweat lodge ceremony, about which most of us here in Arizona are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.44,0:26:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,quite respectful, 560, Ramadan and Hanukkah, Hanukkah, and, okay, so we can forget the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.42,0:26:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,gunas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.18,0:26:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need any gunas today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.98,0:26:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You need any gunas today?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.98,0:26:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.10,0:26:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.50,0:26:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritual progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.07,0:26:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we did this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.57,0:26:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.66,0:26:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional acts are all as a group, 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.44,0:26:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional burning of incense, all these things, genuflection are 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.96,0:27:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The golden rule is at 405, which is above Mexican and Chinese fortune cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.33,0:27:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.33,0:27:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.33,0:27:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can move from fortune cookies to the golden rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.30,0:27:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneeling to prayer, you see anything that indicates devotional supplication to the Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.04,0:27:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 540, saying the rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.23,0:27:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.23,0:27:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay, turning prayer wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.30,0:27:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we'll walk in the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.04,0:27:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we're going to go through, I don't want to go through the levels of consciousness again,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.52,0:27:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think we should just briefly mention them, because I want to get to the farther ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.91,0:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is covered in Transcending Levels of Consciousness, where each level is taken
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.60,0:28:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and what characterizes it, what character traits, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.25,0:28:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At the level of courage, you want to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.28,0:28:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to learn and grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.58,0:28:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So to become spiritually aware, you have to have intention and curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.91,0:28:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop blaming and be concerned about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.02,0:28:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the most important, I think, honesty and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And being steadfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.49,0:28:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what does it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It means stick to it, stick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.70,0:28:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when it seems like you're getting nowhere, just keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.92,0:28:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop worrying about arriving somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep doing this, I will reach that, or do, become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, you see, doing it for some kind of a reward, and you've got to do it for no reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.70,0:28:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe be a good guy for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.79,0:28:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good guy and nobody likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.79,0:29:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people in our culture, you're a good guy, you'd be, they'd throw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.29,0:29:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them their money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them their money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.74,0:29:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw this guy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next is, after courage, of course, is neutral, which is very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it goes this way, and it's okay if it goes that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.08,0:29:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutral, it's okay if you find the button, and it's okay if you go without a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.75,0:29:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to convince her of that this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.01,0:29:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay for you to say, but it wasn't your button.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.64,0:29:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.44,0:29:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutral, it's easy going.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.44,0:29:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.44,0:29:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fired up with ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.44,0:29:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But neutral people are very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.47,0:29:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're agreeable, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.47,0:29:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.47,0:29:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.75,0:30:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a cheeseburger?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.75,0:30:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.75,0:30:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a fish burger?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.75,0:30:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.75,0:30:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.21,0:30:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.21,0:30:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.21,0:30:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you see, they're safe to be with, and that's why they're attractive people, and they're comfortable, comfortable people at neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.21,0:30:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next one above that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.21,0:30:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cordial, and they have a good sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.98,0:30:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Above neutral, what's after neutral?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.98,0:30:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.25,0:30:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.30,0:30:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.30,0:30:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're up to the fortune cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.30,0:30:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To be helpful, to be positive, goodwill towards life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.30,0:30:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think goodwill to life is a very powerful tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't calibrate it, but I think goodwill to all of life is a very powerful tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very positive asset, and we'll move on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.01,0:30:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason, of course, we're very familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.01,0:31:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the world of today, the world of science, technology, the world of education, and the Newtonian level.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.46,0:31:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.46,0:31:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.46,0:31:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need any introduction to science.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At 500, then what happens is we begin to change paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.46,0:31:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We move from the linear, definable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.46,0:31:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From logic, from the dialectic of logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.94,0:31:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 500, you leave logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.94,0:31:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing logical to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.94,0:31:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.94,0:31:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've left logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.94,0:31:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.16,0:31:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.16,0:31:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, now you're in a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.16,0:31:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is why theology and science and consciousness, you see conferences on consciousness and spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.22,0:31:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and consciousness, rather consciousness and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.22,0:31:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see science and consciousness or science and religion or science and theology,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.22,0:32:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it always calibrates around 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.22,0:32:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.22,0:32:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It never seems to get much past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.22,0:32:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And what they don't get is that love, spiritual reality, is a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.93,0:32:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't measure, look for ghosts with a Geiger counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.93,0:32:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.93,0:32:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't measure ghosts with a Geiger counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.93,0:32:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the wrong tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.93,0:32:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is not the tool to investigate spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.93,0:32:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual reality is subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.96,0:32:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.96,0:32:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.96,0:32:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.96,0:32:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove that somebody loves somebody, and yet they'll give up their life for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.96,0:32:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.38,0:32:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is inclusive, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.97,0:32:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cordial.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.97,0:32:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uplifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.97,0:32:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has an innate goodness to itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.97,0:32:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So people in a spiritual evolution reach a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.97,0:32:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They reach a point of sort of a sweet goodness, sort of a sweetness to their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.64,0:32:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.64,0:33:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of cordial towards life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.64,0:33:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.90,0:33:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.90,0:33:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional love at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.90,0:33:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4% of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.90,0:33:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is characteristic of healing groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.90,0:33:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes saintly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.01,0:33:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous begins to occur because the Kundalini energy now gets quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.01,0:33:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 540s.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.01,0:33:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a sensitivity to beauty, which becomes even more almost rapturous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.08,0:33:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And beauty can become overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.01,0:33:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can look at two people sitting and waiting for a plane in an airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.01,0:33:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at each other with a loving look, and it just makes you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.04,0:33:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beauty makes you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.00,0:33:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.00,0:33:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.11,0:33:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Level 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.33,0:34:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.33,0:34:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's an inner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.33,0:34:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a radiant state.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.33,0:34:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It emanates from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.52,0:34:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.53,0:34:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.53,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody talking to you in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a blissful state is the classic term for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.61,0:34:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really quite right either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.61,0:34:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.61,0:34:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a state of absolute fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.61,0:34:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the presence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.61,0:34:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.61,0:34:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just beyond ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.61,0:34:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You go into joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.61,0:34:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you go into ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.71,0:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you surrender ecstasy to God, then this replaces it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.53,0:34:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.53,0:34:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.53,0:34:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.61,0:34:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The famous, the best known, of course, are Nisargadatta Maharaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.82,0:34:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ramana Maharshi, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.98,0:35:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.98,0:35:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonduality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.01,0:35:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is where the self, it is dissolved into the self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.01,0:35:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the grace of the Guru becomes sought because they begin to radiate an energy from 700 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.11,0:35:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They radiate an energy which you pick up in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.25,0:35:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And that becomes then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.25,0:35:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The potential becomes actually possible once there's the vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.25,0:35:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The vibration is necessary because it's a nonlinear dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.25,0:35:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nonlinear dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.63,0:35:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore to have heard about it, known about it, or read about it doesn't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.86,0:35:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you have to have the energy, the frequency, the vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.17,0:35:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the states of samadhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We say they're awakened, enlightened, transcendent states.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.17,0:35:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The sage, the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.17,0:36:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Devoid of needs and witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.98,0:36:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we say they've become sanctified, Mother Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.98,0:36:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.46,0:36:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Devoid of needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.19,0:36:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So one reason those levels are peaceful is because there's nothing you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.19,0:36:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the only time you say you want something is because other people are not happy unless you say you want something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.19,0:36:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you make up something that's plausible and then they're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.78,0:36:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I want a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.36,0:36:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now they're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.73,0:36:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you sacrifice the truth a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.82,0:36:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do want a pound of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.46,0:36:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.46,0:36:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.46,0:36:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.46,0:37:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Full enlightenment then has these peculiar characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.80,0:37:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is not different than that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We said level 850, we've already spoken quite a bit about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.98,0:37:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really a subject in and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.11,0:37:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How to transcend the void, which I've written about several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.11,0:37:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't want any students of mine to land in the void and stay there for a lifetime after a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.11,0:37:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.28,0:37:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say, Dave, you didn't tell them about the void?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.28,0:37:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.63,0:37:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll get it, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.92,0:37:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get it from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.92,0:37:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.92,0:37:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How to transcend the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.59,0:37:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anybody stuck there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.59,0:37:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because you can go into the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.94,0:37:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave this lifetime in the void and come back in and go back out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.94,0:38:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And no memory of any lifetimes in between because you're in the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.07,0:38:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So there weren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.07,0:38:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which saves you a lot of bother in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.07,0:38:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is intrinsic to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.96,0:38:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you realize, when you become identified, no longer the witness, the watcher, the observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is consciousness and that which you are are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.13,0:38:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What goes with consciousness is awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.13,0:38:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But awareness is also an aspect of consciousness and it's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.13,0:38:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.13,0:38:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So when a spiritual teacher is speaking from what's classically called the Purusha,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.13,0:38:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they're talking from the self with a capital S, which has no personal identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.13,0:38:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no person speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.13,0:38:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, a teacher doesn't hear anything from anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.38,0:38:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.61,0:38:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't speak with other forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.69,0:38:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this will probably conflict with some religious teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.69,0:39:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my own experience, there's never been an other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.69,0:39:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other who speaks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.69,0:39:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for an other to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.65,0:39:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what is being spoken about is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.65,0:39:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,An ant doesn't need somebody to tell him you're an ant, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.65,0:39:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What it is, is self-revealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.84,0:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Purusha is the self of the teacher, which speaks only from its own knowingness from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.32,0:39:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have any external with which it communicates.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.32,0:39:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't channel some entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.32,0:39:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't channel an archangel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.32,0:39:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't channel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.67,0:39:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.67,0:39:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.67,0:39:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is already is complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.67,0:39:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It radiates out its completeness and its totality as a radiance, as a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.01,0:40:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-fulfilling knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.01,0:40:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That which speaks and that which is spoken of are identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.01,0:40:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.01,0:40:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-dualistic, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.13,0:40:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are the levels of 850 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.48,0:40:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So this oneness, anyway, these are just words, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.48,0:40:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.48,0:40:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.53,0:40:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.98,0:40:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier, it's easier to be it than it is to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.17,0:40:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, of course, you all understand what it is because we all share it every time we get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.17,0:40:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.30,0:40:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.05,0:40:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, these are all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.90,0:40:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.90,0:40:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.90,0:40:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-volitional.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.90,0:40:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.90,0:40:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.90,0:40:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You verbalize it in order to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.90,0:40:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which verbalizes it, I always call it the persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.90,0:41:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of an aspect of energy that is called up when there's a purpose for communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.09,0:41:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And it speaks autonomously and spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.09,0:41:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to think about what to say because there's nobody saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.09,0:41:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The speakingness is already its own speakingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.09,0:41:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The speakingness is fulfilled already.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.09,0:41:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the speakingness that is speaking, which is hard to understand in ordinary predicate and subject languaging in English, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.53,0:41:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But the speakingness is what is speaking, is all you can say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And people either get it or they don't, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.53,0:41:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like lovingness is loving, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.53,0:41:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't a dualistic thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.57,0:41:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The lovingness is its own expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.57,0:41:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the expression of what it is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.57,0:41:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on because we have to get to where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.57,0:41:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We made obligations as spiritual teachers, which nobody's ever done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.57,0:42:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time, a couple of thousand years too late if you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.15,0:42:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that the person should be willing to make a declaration of responsibility about their integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.15,0:42:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,about their obligation, the stewardship of their knowledge, the moral and ethical conduct with students,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.15,0:42:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which is outrageous all over the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.28,0:42:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The refusal to exploit people's, any aspect of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.28,0:42:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The commitment to explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.28,0:42:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To provide, maintain availability, to be the steward of the availability of the teachings, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.28,0:42:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some didn't get written down for a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.28,0:42:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time they got written down, they had wandered far from the original truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.28,0:42:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A good teacher, you know, dissuades people from becoming teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.46,0:42:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They become dependent.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.46,0:42:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And likes to see autonomous study groups, which we have them all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.61,0:42:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Acknowledges the source of the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.61,0:42:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no person doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.61,0:43:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there's no personal credit because there's no person to take credit or claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.61,0:43:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who would take credit or claim unless they thought there was some separate person there
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.82,0:43:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to whom adulation was due, you know what I mean?
