Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.94,0:43:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.94,0:43:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, so there's no personal credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.42,0:43:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, the student owes you nothing at all.
