Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Obligation of spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.36,0:43:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Provide a means of verification of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.61,0:43:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to take somebody's word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.61,0:44:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to push people's credibility.
